guna mengakses bersamaan?**  - [ ] Indexing - [ ] Sharding - [x] Concurrency Control / Locking - [ ] Backup  </div> ', NULL, '{}', 5, 'published', datetime('now'), datetime('now'), 'd77faaca-a25b-4673-bc7f-c66754ed7fd3', 'bed8b13a-6e3d-4c76-bcbe-d7ca8838bbdd', NULL, '17-advanced-database-quiz', NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 0.0, NULL, NULL, 'default');;
