](quiz.md) - [OpenAI Prompt Guide](https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/prompt-engineering) - [Cursor AI](https://cursor.sh) ', NULL, '{}', 5, 'published', datetime('now'), datetime('now'), '50cec631-9b51-4736-9b9a-af18c5ff22b8', 'd6e49a13-6660-4083-9ea5-d30c74e41374', NULL, '18-ai-prompt-engineering-cheatsheet', NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 0.0, NULL, NULL, 'default');;
