Federation = GraphQL gateway yang gabungin beberapa **subgraph** jadi satu **supergraph**. Cocok buat microservices.

### Arsitektur

```
         ┌──────────────┐
         │   Gateway     │ ← supergraph schema
         │ (Apollo Router)│
         └──┬────┬────┬──┘
