  VALUES ('b813b4a8-c23f-4cb9-b0f9-ae14d861fa70', 'text', 'Sesi 3: LinkedIn & Career', '# Sesi 3: LinkedIn & Career  > Optimasi profil LinkedIn dan CV untuk menarik perekrut, plus bangun personal branding statement yang kuat.  **Durasi**: 4 jam | **Output**: Profil LinkedIn optimal + CV siap pakai  ---  ## 3.1 LinkedIn Profile Optimization  Profil LinkedIn yang optimal meningkatkan visibilitas di pencarian perekrut hingga 40x.  ### Headline  Headline muncul di bawah nama — ini elemen pertama dilihat perekrut.  **Format optimal:** ``` [Jabatan] | [Spesialisasi] | [Skill Utama] | [Value Proposition] ```  **Contoh:**  | ❌ Kurang Baik | ✅ Optimal | |----------------|-----------| | Frontend Developer at PT Maju | Frontend Developer | React & TypeScript | Building Performant Web Apps | | Mahasiswa | Computer Science Student | Full-Stack Dev | React | Python | Building for Impact | | Looking for job | Frontend Developer | 3+ Years Exp | React Specialist | Open to Work |  ### About Section (2-3 paragraf)  **Template Paragraf 1 — Hook:** > "Frontend Developer with [angka] years of experience building [jenis aplikasi] using [teknologi utama]. Passionate about creating [value] through [pendekatan teknis]."  **Template Paragraf 2 — Bukti:** > "At [perusahaan/proyek], I [action verb] [what you did], resulting in [angka hasil]. Previously at [previous role/project], I [achievement lain]."  **Template Paragraf 3 — CTA:** > "Currently exploring opportunities in [bidang/industri]. Open to [jenis kolaborasi]. Let''s connect if you''re interested in [topik]!"  ### Featured Section  Gunakan fitur **Featured** untuk menampilkan:  1. **Portfolio website** — tambahkan link ke live site 2. **GitHub profile** — tambahkan link GitHub 3. **Artikel atau project** — tambahkan post/case study 4. **Sertifikasi** — screenshots sertifikat  Cara: Buka profil → Klik **Add a featured section** → Pilih Media / Links / Posts  ### Skills & Endorsement  Strategi skills endorsement:  - **Pilih 5-10 skill utama** yang relevan dengan target karir - Susun urutan skill — skill paling kuat di atas - **Minta endorsement** dari teman, rekan kerja, dosen - Ambil **LinkedIn Skill Assessment** untuk dapat badge "Skill Verified"  **Skill Wajib Developer:** | Kategori | Skill | |----------|-------| | Bahasa | JavaScript, TypeScript, Python, Go | | Frontend | React, Next.js, Vue, Tailwind CSS | | Backend | Node.js, Express, Django, PostgreSQL | | Tools | Git, Docker, CI/CD, AWS, Figma | | Soft Skills | Problem Solving, Team Collaboration, Communication |  ### Experience Section  Format bullet untuk job/project experience:  ``` [Action Verb] + [What you did] + [How you did it] + [Result/Impact] ```  **Contoh:** - Developed responsive web dashboard using React and TypeScript, reducing page load time by 35% - Led migration from REST to GraphQL API, improving data fetching efficiency by 50% across 10+ endpoints - Collaborated with 5 cross-functional team members to ship 3 major features in Q1 2026  ### Action Verbs (dari ATS-friendly)  | Kategori | Verbs | |----------|-------| | Leadership | Led, Directed, Spearheaded, Coordinated, Managed | | Development | Built, Developed, Engineered, Architected, Implemented | | Analysis | Analyzed, Evaluated, Assessed, Optimized, Audited | | Design | Designed, Created, Architected, Structured, Formulated | | Improvement | Improved, Enhanced, Streamlined, Transformed, Refactored |  ### Connection Strategy  - **Target 500+ connections** — threshold LinkedIn "All-Star" profile - Kirim **personalized connection request** - Contoh: *"Hi [name], Saya melihat background kamu di [bidang]. Saya juga tertarik di [topik]. Would love to connect and follow your journey!"* - **Engage** — like, comment, share post minimal 3x seminggu  ---  ## 3.2 ATS-Friendly CV / Resume  ATS (Applicant Tracking System) adalah software yang membaca CV secara otomatis. 75% CV ditolak ATS sebelum dilihat manusia.  ### Format ATS Checklist  | Aturan | ✅ Lakukan | ❌ Jangan | |--------|-----------|-----------| | Font | Arial, Calibri, Roboto (10-12pt) | Script, decorative, gambar font | | File | **PDF** (save as standard PDF) | JPG, PNG, Canva export (images) | | Structure | Single column, clear headings | Multi-column, tables, text boxes | | Section | Standard: Summary → Experience → Education → Skills | Creative layouts, icons as bullets | | Keywords | Match job description keywords | Generic skills without context | | Header | Nama + phone + email + LinkedIn + GitHub | Foto, alamat lengkap, tanggal lahir |  ### Template CV ATS-Friendly  ``` [NAMA LENGKAP] [Phone] | [Email] | linkedin.com/in/[username] | github.com/[username] [Portfolio URL]  --- PROFESSIONAL SUMMARY [2-3 kalimat: role + experience + key skills + target]  EXPERIENCE [Job Title] | [Company] | [Location] [Month Year] – [Month Year]  - [Action verb] [task] using [tools], resulting in [metric] - [Action verb] [task] using [tools], resulting in [metric] - [Action verb] [task] using [tools], resulting in [metric]  [Previous Job Title] | [Company] | [Location] [Month Year] – [Month Year]  - [Same format — action, tool, result] - ...  EDUCATION [Degree] in [Major] | [University] [Year] – [Year] - GPA: [value] (optional) - Relevant coursework: [list]  PROJECTS [Project Name] — [Tech Stack] - Brief description + impact - Link: github.com/username/project  SKILLS Languages: JavaScript, TypeScript, Python Frameworks: React, Next.js, Node.js, Express Tools: Git, Docker, AWS, PostgreSQL, Figma  CERTIFICATIONS - [Cert Name] | [Issuer] | [Year] - [Cert Name] | [Issuer] | [Year]  --- ```  ### Achievement with Numbers  Ganti deskripsi tugas biasa dengan achievement yang terukur:  | ❌ Tugas Biasa | ✅ Achievement Terukur | |----------------|----------------------| | Developed website using React | Built React dashboard with 15+ components, serving 1,000+ daily users | | Fixed bugs in codebase | Identified and resolved 40+ production bugs, improving app stability by 30% | | Worked on team projects | Collaborated in 5-person agile team to deliver 3 sprints on time | | Wrote unit tests | Achieved 85% code coverage with 200+ unit tests using Jest | | Improved performance | Optimized API queries reducing response time from 2.3s to 0.4s (82% faster) |  ### One-Page Rule  CV maksimal **1 halaman** untuk < 10 tahun pengalaman. Cara ringkas:  - Hanya 5-7 bullet terbaik per role - Hilangkan deskripsi tugas yang obvious - Gabungkan proyek kecil jadi satu section - Gunakan angka untuk highlight impact  ---  ## 3.3 Personal Branding Statement  Personal branding statement adalah satu kalimat yang menjelaskan: siapa kamu, apa yang kamu lakukan, dan kenapa itu penting.  ### Formula  ``` I help [target audience] [achieve outcome] through [your expertise/method]. ```  **Contoh:** - "I help startups build fast, accessible web applications using React and TypeScript." - "I help businesses turn complex data into actionable insights with clean dashboards." - "I help junior developers transition into tech through structured mentoring and real-world projects."  ### Untuk LinkedIn Headline  ``` [Role] | [Skill 1] + [Skill 2] | [Impact Statement] ```  **Contoh:** - "Frontend Developer | React + TypeScript | Building performant web apps" - "Software Engineer | Node.js + PostgreSQL | Scaling backend systems" - "UI/UX Developer | Figma → React | Designing & building user-centric interfaces"  ### Untuk CV Summary  ``` [Role] with [X years] experience in [field]. Specialized in [skill 1], [skill 2], and [skill 3].  Proven track record of [achievement type], including [specific result].  Seeking to leverage [strength] at [target company type]. ```  **Contoh:** > "Frontend Developer with 3+ years experience in building web applications. Specialized in React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS. Proven track record of improving user experience and performance, including reducing page load time by 40% and increasing user engagement by 25%. Seeking to leverage modern frontend expertise at a fast-growing SaaS company."  ---  ## 3.4 LinkedIn Profile Checklist  Gunakan checklist sebelum dianggap selesai:  - [ ] **Profile photo** profesional (bukan selfie, bukan liburan) - [ ] **Background banner** relevan (tech theme, personal brand) - [ ] **Headline** mengandung keyword pencarian role target - [ ] **About section** 3 paragraf (hook, bukti, CTA) - [ ] **Featured** — minimal 2 item (portfolio, GitHub, artikel) - [ ] **Experience** — semua bullet pakai action verb + angka - [ ] **Education** — diisi lengkap - [ ] **Skills** — minimal 5 skill, urut sesuai prioritas - [ ] **Licenses & Certifications** — diisi jika ada - [ ] **URL** — custom LinkedIn URL (`linkedin.com/in/namakamu`) - [ ] **Open to Work** — aktif (bisa visible ke semua atau hanya recruiters)  ---  ## ✍️ Latihan  ### Latihan 1: Optimasi Headline & About  Buka profil LinkedIn kamu (atau buat draft).  1. Tulis **headline** baru menggunakan format: `[Role] | [Skill 1] + [Skill 2] | [Value Proposition]` 2. Tulis **About section** 3 paragraf:    - Paragraf 1: Hook — siapa kamu dan apa yang kamu lakukan    - Paragraf 2: Bukti — pencapaian dengan angka    - Paragraf 3: CTA — apa yang kamu cari 3. Kirim ke teman/dosen untuk feedback  **Kriteria**: Headline mengandung keyword yang bisa dicari perekrut, about section maksimal 300 kata.  ### Latihan 2: Rewrite Experience Bullets  Ambil 3 pengalaman (kerja/ magang/ organisasi/ proyek kampus) kamu.  Untuk setiap pengalaman, tulis ulang bullet points menggunakan format: ``` [Action Verb] + [What] + [Tools] + [Result with numbers] ```  **Contoh transformasi:** | Sebelum | Sesudah | |---------|---------| | "Membuat website company profile" | "Built company profile website using React and Tailwind CSS, resulting in 40% increase in online inquiries" | | "Mengelola database" | "Managed PostgreSQL database with 10+ tables, serving 500+ daily transactions with 99.9% uptime" |  **Kriteria**: Minimal 9 bullet (3 per role), setiap bullet ada angka/impact.  ### Latihan 3: Buat CV ATS-Friendly  Gunakan template ATS-friendly dari section 3.2. Isi dengan data diri:  1. Professional Summary (2-3 kalimat) 2. Experience (minimal 1 role, 3 bullets per role) 3. Education 4. Projects (minimal 2) 5. Skills (kategorikan: Languages, Frameworks, Tools) 6. Certifications (jika ada)  Export sebagai PDF. Cek menggunakan [resumeworded.com](https://resumeworded.com) atau tools serupa.  **Kriteria**: Single column, no images/icons, 1 page, PDF format, ATS score minimal 70.  ### Latihan 4: Personal Branding Statement + All-Star Profile  1. Tulis **personal branding statement** menggunakan formula:    `I help [target] [outcome] through [method].` 2. Tulis ulang **LinkedIn headline** berdasarkan statement tersebut 3. Apply **LinkedIn profile checklist** (section 3.4) — pastikan semua centang terpenuhi 4. Kirim **personalized connection request** ke 5 orang di bidang yang sama  **Kriteria**: Personal branding statement jelas dan spesifik (bukan generik), LinkedIn profile minimal level "Intermediate" atau "All-Star", connection request tidak copy-paste massal. ', NULL, '{}', 3, 'published', datetime('now'), datetime('now'), 'b094f56f-5f96-4059-8d67-2803f7add8fa', 'bd6bf1d8-dad3-45bc-8928-dedf61db9cba', NULL, '03-linkedin-career', NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 0.0, NULL, NULL, 'default');;
VALUES ('21dac2c2-88dd-4794-9d38-23cf99a1c5c7', 'text', 'Sesi 4: Tech Community & Open Source', '# Sesi 4: Tech Community & Open Source

> Tulis artikel teknis, berkontribusi ke open source, dan bangun jaringan di komunitas tech.

**Durasi**: 4 jam | **Output**: Artikel blog + PR open source

---

## 4.1 Technical Blogging

Blog teknis membangun authority dan personal branding. Tiga platform utama:

### Platform Blog

| Platform | Kelebihan | Kekurangan | Target Audience |
|----------|-----------|------------|-----------------|
| **Dev.to** | Komunitas developer besar, sudah ada pembaca, SEO bagus | Kurang kontrol kustomisasi | Developer global |
| **Hashnode** | Own domain, built-in newsletter, modern UI | Komunitas lebih kecil dari Dev.to | Tech founders, builders |
| **Medium** | Trafik tinggi, monetisasi partner program | Tidak bisa custom domain gratis, kurang "tech vibe" | General tech audience |

### Cara Mulai Blog di Dev.to

1. Buka [dev.to](https://dev.to/) → Sign up with GitHub
2. Klik profil → **Create Post**
3. Tulis artikel menggunakan Markdown
4. Tambahkan tag (maks 4, misal: `react`, `typescript`, `tutorial`, `webdev`)
5. Set **Canonical URL** jika blog juga di posting di tempat lain
6. Klik **Publish** atau **Save as draft**

### Cara Mulai Blog di Hashnode

1. Buka [hashnode.com](https://hashnode.com/) → Sign up
2. Buat blog: pilih nama, URL, dan tema
3. Mulai nulis di dashboard → **New Story**
4. Opsional: hubungkan custom domain (misal: `blog.namakamu.com`)

---

## 4.2 Menulis Artikel Teknis

### Struktur Artikel Efektif

```
📝 Struktur Artikel Teknis yang Engaging

1. JUDUL
   - Formula: [Angka] + [Adjective] + [Keyword] + [Promise]
   - Contoh: "10 React Hooks yang Wajib Dikuasai Developer 2026"
   - Contoh: "How I Reduced Build Time by 60% with Vite Migration"

2. COVER IMAGE
   - Buat cover sederhana pakai Canva / Figma
   - Ukuran standar: 1200×628px

3. INTRO (Hook)
   - Problem: apa yang reader alami
   - Empathy: "Saya juga pernah ngalamin ini..."
   - Solution: apa yang akan mereka dapatkan setelah baca

4. PRASYARAT
   - Skill/ tools yang reader harus punya
   - Link ke artikel terkait jika ada

5. TUTORIAL / PEMBAHASAN UTAMA
   - Step-by-step jelas
   - Tiap step: why → how → code
   - Gunakan code blocks dengan syntax highlighting

6. CODE SNIPPET
   ```javascript
   // Always explain what the code does BEFORE showing it
   const handleSubmit = async (data) => {
     const result = await api.post(''/users'', data);
  VALUES ('ee53ba50-33b3-423a-9df3-08c3e4c8f0f6', 'text', '🧠 Cheatsheet', '# 🧠 Cheatsheet: Digital Portfolio & Personal Branding  > Referensi cepet — 1 halaman. Modul 44: GitHub profile, portfolio website, LinkedIn optimization, tech community.  ## Topik Utama  | Sesi | Topik | Tools | |------|-------|-------| | 01 | GitHub Profesional — Profile README, pinned repos, badge shields.io, project docs, GitHub Pages | Shields.io, GitHub Pages | | 02 | Portfolio Website — Hero, about, project cards, skills, contact form, case study pages, deploy | Vercel, Netlify | | 03 | LinkedIn & Career — Optimasi profil, headline, about, featured projects, CV ATS-friendly | LinkedIn | | 04 | Tech Community — Blog teknis (Dev.to/Hashnode), problem-solution articles, open source PR, networking | Dev.to, Hashnode |  ## Command / Sintaks Penting  ### GitHub Profile README  ```bash # Buat repo special: username/username mkdir username && cd username # Buat README.md — ini jadi profile README  # Badge generator # https://rahuldkjain.github.io/gh-profile-readme-generator/ # https://shields.io/ ```  **Badge format:** ```markdown ![JavaScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/JavaScript-F7DF1E?style=for-the-badge&logo=javascript&logoColor=black) ![Node.js](https://img.shields.io/badge/Node.js-339933?style=for-the-badge&logo=node.js&logoColor=white) ![React](https://img.shields.io/badge/React-20232A?style=for-the-badge&logo=react&logoColor=61DAFB) ```  **GitHub Stats:** ```markdown ![GitHub Stats](https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api?username=USERNAME&show_icons=true&theme=radical) ![Top Languages](https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api/top-langs/?username=USERNAME&layout=compact&theme=radical) ![GitHub Streak](https://streak-stats.demolab.com?user=USERNAME) ```  **Pinned repos:** ```markdown <!-- Pin 6 repos di GitHub profile settings --> <!-- Tips: pin projek yang beda-beda tech stack --> ```  ### Portfolio Website Structure  ``` index.html          → Hero + About + Contact projects.html       → Project cards grid case-study/         → Individual project deep-dive skills.html         → Skills progress bar contact.html        → Contact form (Formspree/Formsubmit) ```  **Essential sections:** ```html <!-- Hero Section --> <section class="hero">   <h1>Hi, I''m [Name] 👋</h1>   <p>Full-stack developer specializing in [tech].</p>   <a href="#projects">View My Work</a> </section>  <!-- Project Card --> <div class="project-card">   <img src="project-screenshot.webp" alt="Project Name" loading="lazy">   <h3>Project Name</h3>   <p>Brief description. Problem solved.</p>   <div class="tech-tags">     <span>React</span><span>Node.js</span><span>PostgreSQL</span>   </div>   <div class="project-links">     <a href="live-url">Live Demo</a>     <a href="github-url">Source Code</a>   </div> </div> ```  ### Deploy Portfolio  ```bash # Vercel npx vercel --prod  # Netlify npx netlify deploy --prod  # GitHub Pages (gratis, khusus static) # Settings → Pages → Source: main branch /docs folder ```  ### LinkedIn Optimization  **Headline formula:** ``` [Role] | [Specialization] | [Impact/Value] ``` Contoh: `Full-Stack Developer | React & Node.js | Building Scalable Web Apps`  **About section structure:** ``` 1. Hook (1-2 kalimat — siapa, apa yang bikin beda) 2. What I do (spesialisasi + tech stack) 3. Achievement (metrics: "reduced load time by 40%", "served 10k+ users") 4. What I''m looking for (open to opportunities / collaboration) 5. Call to action (email, portfolio link) ```  **CV ATS Tips:** - Gunakan section headings standar: Experience, Education, Skills - Hindari kolom/tables — ATS gak bisa baca - Pakai action verbs: Built, Implemented, Optimized, Reduced - Quantify achievements: "Improved API response time from 800ms to 200ms" - File format: PDF (bukan DOCX yang formatting-nya bisa pecah)  ### Tech Blog Structure  ```markdown # [Problem-Solving Article Title]  ## The Problem [1-2 paragraf: what problem you faced, context]  ## The Solution [Approach + why you chose this solution]  ## Implementation [Code snippets + explanation]  ## Results [Metrics, screenshots, demo link]  ## Conclusion [Key takeaways, what you''d do differently] ```  **Publish platforms:** - **Dev.to** — community besar, markdown editor, dev-focused - **Hashnode** — custom domain, SEO-friendly, newsletter - **Medium** — audiens umum, paywall optional  ### Open Source Contributions  ```bash # Cari issue "good first issue" # https://github.com/topics/good-first-issue  # Fork → Clone → Branch → Code → PR git fork https://github.com/owner/repo.git git checkout -b fix/issue-123 # ... make changes ... git commit -m "fix: resolve #123 — [description]" git push origin fix/issue-123 # Create PR di GitHub ```  ## Tips & Trik  - **GitHub README** = first impression — badge visual, stats, pinned repos yang beda-beda - **Portfolio** harus live di URL profesional — `yourname.dev` > `github.io/username` - **Case study > list** — ceritakan problem → approach → result, bukan cuma fitur - **Mobile-first** — recruiter sering cek portfolio dari HP - **Loading time < 3s** — optimasi gambar (WebP), lazy load, minimal JS - **LinkedIn headline** = SEO keywords — recruiter search by keywords - **Quantify everything** — "improved performance" vs "reduced API latency from 800ms to 200ms" - **1 blog per 2 weeks** > 10 artikel sekaligus — konsistensi matters - **Open source PR** — bahkan typo fix pun valid contribution  ## Common Mistakes  - ❌ **README kosong** — missed opportunity untuk personal branding - ❌ **Portfolio cuma screenshot** — gak ada link live atau source code - ❌ **Gak ada CTA di portfolio** — recruiter harus tau cara contact kamu - ❌ **LinkedIn headline default** — "Student at [University]" → gak SEO-friendly - ❌ **CV 5 halaman** — 1-2 halaman max, ATS-friendly format - ❌ **No metrics di achievement** — "Built an API" vs "Built REST API serving 50k req/day with 99.9% uptime" - ❌ **Blog tanpa code** — tech articles butuh code demonstration - ❌ **Portfolio gak responsive** — recruiter check dari HP - ❌ **Gak update LinkedIn** — stale profile = invisible to recruiters - ❌ **Waiting untuk "siap"** — ship portfolio sekarang, iterate nanti  ## Link Cepat  - [Module README](.) - [Sesi 01 — GitHub Profesional](01-github-profile.md) - [Sesi 02 — Portfolio Website](02-portfolio-website.md) - [Sesi 03 — LinkedIn & Career](03-linkedin-career.md) - [Sesi 04 — Tech Community](04-tech-community.md) - [Quiz](quiz.md) - [GitHub Profile README Generator](https://rahuldkjain.github.io/gh-profile-readme-generator/) - [Shields.io](https://shields.io/) - [Vercel](https://vercel.com/) - [Dev.to](https://dev.to/) ', NULL, '{}', 5, 'published', datetime('now'), datetime('now'), 'b094f56f-5f96-4059-8d67-2803f7add8fa', 'bd6bf1d8-dad3-45bc-8928-dedf61db9cba', NULL, '44-portfolio-branding-cheatsheet', NULL, 0, 1, NULL, 0.0, NULL, NULL, 'default');;
